{
  "texts": [
    "We presented use case experiments to show that the current version of the CT-EBM-SP corpus allowed us testing state-of-the-art neural biomedical named entity recognizers with competitive results.",
    "The presented methods are generalizable to other languages such as English, French or German, for which similar sources are available.We believe this work contributes to enhancing the access to evidence-based information for both health professionals and patients.",
    "We would also be very satisfied if this resource played a beneficial role for developing systems that help patients to understand trial protocols, interventions and procedures better.",
    "Fig. 1 Fig.",
    "1 Sample of the annotation Fig. 33Fig."
  ]
